## 七、YAML DSL 设计

### scenario 示例

路径：`cases/scenario/kyc.submit-and-approve.yaml`

```yaml
case_id: kyc_submit_and_approve
case_name: 企业认证 KYC 提交并由管理端审核
description: user 端提交企业认证，admin 端审核通过，最后 user 端回查状态
mode: hybrid

sessions:
  - name: user
    login_url: "${env.USER_LOGIN_URL}"
    username: "${env.USER_USERNAME}"
    password: "${env.USER_PASSWORD}"
  - name: admin
    login_url: "${env.ADMIN_LOGIN_URL}"
    username: "${env.ADMIN_USERNAME}"
    password: "${env.ADMIN_PASSWORD}"

variables:
  enterprise_name: "${env.KYC_ENTERPRISE_NAME_PREFIX}_${timestamp}"
  license_no: "${env.KYC_LICENSE_NO_PREFIX}_${timestamp}"
  legal_person: "${env.KYC_LEGAL_PERSON}"
  id_card_no: "${env.KYC_ID_CARD_NO}"
  review_remark: "${env.KYC_REVIEW_REMARK}"

locations:
  file: "cases/location/kyc.submit-and-approve.yaml"

steps:
  - step_id: user_open_login
    name: user 打开登录页
    type: web_open
    session: user
    url: "${session.login_url}"
  - step_id: user_login
    name: user 登录
    type: flow_login
    session: user
    username: "${session.username}"
    password: "${session.password}"
  - step_id: user_open_kyc
    name: user 进入 KYC 页面
    type: web_click
    session: user
    target: user_kyc_menu
  - step_id: user_fill_enterprise_name
    name: 填写企业名称
    type: web_input
    session: user
    target: kyc_enterprise_name
    value: "${var.enterprise_name}"
  - step_id: user_submit_kyc
    name: 提交 KYC 审核
    type: web_click
    session: user
    target: kyc_submit
  - step_id: user_assert_pending
    name: 断言 user 端状态为审核中
    type: web_assert_text
    session: user
    target: kyc_status
    expected: "审核中"
  - step_id: admin_open_login
    name: admin 打开登录页
    type: web_open
    session: admin
    url: "${session.login_url}"
  - step_id: admin_login
    name: admin 登录
    type: flow_login
    session: admin
    username: "${session.username}"
    password: "${session.password}"
  - step_id: admin_open_kyc_review
    name: admin 进入 KYC 审核列表
    type: web_click
    session: admin
    target: admin_kyc_menu
  - step_id: admin_search_kyc
    name: admin 搜索 KYC 记录
    type: web_input
    session: admin
    target: admin_kyc_search_input
    value: "${var.enterprise_name}"
  - step_id: admin_approve
    name: admin 点击审核通过
    type: web_click
    session: admin
    target: admin_kyc_approve_button
  - step_id: user_reload_kyc
    name: user 刷新 KYC 页面
    type: web_reload
    session: user
  - step_id: user_assert_approved
    name: 断言 user 端状态为审核通过
    type: web_assert_text
    session: user
    target: kyc_status
    expected: "审核通过"
```

